
allocPSA

Installation Guide


The manual prodecure

 - Ensure correct PHP settings
 - Ensure mysql > 3.23
 - Get apache document root 
 - Get php include_path 
 - Put source in document root
 - run installer script /webroot/alloc/util/install.sh
 - Install database structure and meta data
 - Install cron jobs
 - Put alloc.inc into include path





